verse = \lyricmode {
 The peo -- ple who in dark -- ness walked 
have seen a glo -- rious light; 
now day has dawned for those who dwelt 
in death's sur -- round -- ing night. 
To hail you, Sun of Right -- eous -- ness, 
they with re -- joic -- ing come 
as when with joy they share the spoil 
or bear the har -- vest home. 
}
